      "content": "i know there are people to talk to, but it's not about \"treatment.\" it's just that the more i try to find myself, the more i realize there's nothing to find. the person everyone sees is just a mask, and i'm so tired of holding it up. if the person behind the mask isn't even real, then the whole thing is just a mistake. it wouldn't be a tragedy if the performance just... stopped. it would just be a relief.",
